				\begin{document}$$\frac{{\mathop {\sum }\nolimits_{ijk,i \ne k} N_{ij} \times N_{ik}}}{{\mathop {\sum }\nolimits_{jk,j \ne k} T_j \times T_k}}$$\end{document}∑ijk,i≠kNij×Nik∑jk,j≠kTj×Tkwhere Nij and Nik are the copy numbers of clone i observed in independent replicate PCR libraries, j and k, generated from independent aliquots of template DNA and Tj and Tk are total read numbers in the corresponding replicate libraries. The log base 10 of this score is shown in the figures.
